<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <!-- Compiled and minified CSS -->

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.6/css/materialize.min.css">

  <title>WHERE BOOTY??</title>
</head>



<body>

  <div class="whole-box">
    <!-- <div class="darken">
    </div> -->

    <p class="main-title">WHERE BE ME BOOTY?</p>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="description-text col m6 offset-m6 s10 offset-s1">
        <p>Arr, ye League of Legends summoners be having trouble hunting down 
        yer mastery treasure chests? Wander no more! Input ye summoner name and 
        region below, and find which champions still be harboring chests for the 
        earning!</p>
        <p>Built for Riot Games's API Challenge 3.0. Riot allows summoners to 
        earn one chest per champ per season. Utilizes champion mastery data
        to present top performing champions for earning mastery chests. To view
        source code, please visit <a href="https://github.com/territorialFerry/wherebooty">GitHub</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col m6 offset-m6 s12">

          <form action="/wherebooty/data" class="col m10 offset-m1 white-text s12" method="get">

            <div class="input-field col m12 s12">
              <input placeholder="input here" id="first_name" type="text" class="validate" name="username" required>
              {{#if error}}
                <label for="first_name">USERNAME (username not found...)</label>
              {{else}}
              <label for="first_name">USERNAME</label>
              {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="input-field col m12 s12">
              <select name="region">
                <!-- <option value="" disabled selected>Choose your option</option> -->
                <option value="na">na</option>
                <option value="br">br</option>
                <option value="eune">eune</option>
                <option value="euw">euw</option>
                <option value="jp">jp</option>
                <option value="kr">kr</option>
                <option value="lan">lan</option>
                <option value="las">las</option>
                <option value="oce">oce</option>
                <option value="ru">ru</option>
                <option value="tr">tr</option>
              </select>
              <label>Input Region</label>
            </div>

            <br>
            <div class="col s8 offset-s2">
              <button class="btn waves-effect waves-orange deep-orange lighten-5 black-text" type="submit">Submit
              </button>
            </div>



          </form>
        

      </div>
    </div>



  </div>

</body>

<style>
.whole-box {
  background-image: url("http://randomwallpapers.net/league-of-legends-gangplank-lol-1920x1080-wallpaper105828.jpg");
  vertical-align: middle;
  position: relative;
  display: table;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100vh;
  background-size: cover;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.main-title {
  text-align: right;
  color: white;
  font-family: "Roboto";
  font-size: 50px;
  margin-right: 30px;
}

.description-text {
  color: white;
  font-family: "Roboto";
  font-size: 14px;
}

a:link    {color:grey;}  /* unvisited link  */
a:visited {color:grey;}  /* visited link    */
a:hover   {color:grey;}  /* mouse over link */
a:active  {color:grey;}  /* selected link   */ 

.test {
  background-color: white;
}

/* label color */
 .input-field label {
   color: white;
 }
 /* label focus color */
 .input-field input[type=text]:focus + label {
   color: white;
 }
 /* label underline focus color */
 .input-field input[type=text]:focus {
   border-bottom: 1px solid white;
   box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 white;
 }
 /* valid color */
 .input-field input[type=text].valid {
   border-bottom: 1px solid white;
   box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 white;
 }
 /* invalid color */
 .input-field input[type=text].invalid {
   border-bottom: 1px solid white;
   box-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 white;
 }
 /* icon prefix focus color */
 .input-field .prefix.active {
   color: white;
 }




</style>

<script   src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.1.1.min.js"></script>

<!-- Compiled and minified JavaScript -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/0.97.6/js/materialize.min.js"></script>

<script>
  $(document).ready(function() {
    $('select').material_select();
  });
</script>

</html>